<<if _check eq 8>><<set $hunt.room to clone($bathroomTwo)>><</if>>
<<if _check eq 9>><<set $hunt.room to clone($basement)>><</if>>
<</link>>@@
<<else>>@@.mc-thoughts; Level 3+ required@@
<</if>>
<</nobr>>
